This nationalist action has been held every year on National Unity Day since 2005.
When asked by sociologists "Have you heard about the fact that on November 4 in Russia "Russian Marches" are held under the slogans of protecting the rights of Russians in Russia?", three-quarters (75%) of citizens answered in the negative.
Now only one in five Russians knows about this action (20%).
